description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene ("Streptomyces alni" (Woronin 1866) Fiuczek 1959; Actinomyces alni; Aktinomyces alni; Frankia subtilis; Frankiella alni; Nocardia alni; Plasmodiophora alni; Proactinomyces alni; Schinzia alni.
